<article id="post-3370" class="post-3370 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-blog category-w-pogoni-za-winem-czyli-podroze-male-i-duze tag-bolonia tag-emilia-romania tag-kuchnia-wloska tag-wina tag-wino tag-wino-wloskie tag-wlochy">
<header class="entry-header">
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="screen-reader-text">Opublikowane w</span> <a href="http://www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/?p=3370" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2019-03-27T09:42:36+00:00">27/03/2019</time></a></div><!-- .entry-meta --><h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/?p=3370" rel="bookmark">Bolonia &#8211; miasto, ktore trzeba zjesc</a></h3>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a href="http://www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/?p=3370">
<img width="2000" height="1200" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?resize=2000%2C1200" class="attachment-twentyseventeen-featured-image size-twentyseventeen-featured-image wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?zoom=2&amp;resize=2000%2C1200 4000w, https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?zoom=3&amp;resize=2000%2C1200 6000w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px" data-attachment-id="3393" data-permalink="http://www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/?attachment_id=3393" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?fit=4000%2C3008" data-orig-size="4000,3008" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;H3113&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;34,34,135,148.342209&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1552304996&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.22&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;40&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00058038305281486&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;34,34,135,148.342209&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="34,34,135,148.342209" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?fit=300%2C226" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DSC_0306.jpg?fit=525%2C395" />			</a>
</div><!-- .post-thumbnail -->

<div class="entry-content">
<p>Jezeli zapytasz Wlocha, gdzie dobrze zjesc w Italii, to po zarekomendowaniu kuchni swojej mamy istnieje duze prawdopodobienstwo, ze skieruje cie do <strong>Emilii-Romanii</strong> i jej stolicy &#8211; <strong>Bolonii</strong>. Emilia-Romania to chyba najslynniejszy wloski region, jesli chodzi o gastronomie tego kraju. Kulturowa stolica polnocnych Wloch jaka jest Bolonia, ma do zaoferowania mnostwo atrakcji zarowno w kwestii wysmienitego jedzenia, wina, jak i wspanialej sztuki oraz architektury, ktore stanowia chlube nie tylko samego miasta, ale i calego regionu.  <a href="http://www.winozesmakiem.net.pl/?p=3370#more-3370" class="more-link">Czytaj dalej<span class="screen-reader-text"> Bolonia &#8211; miasto, ktore trzeba zjesc</span></a></p>
</div><!-- .entry-content -->


